eu.europa.esig.dss.xades

Class XPathQueryHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.europa.esig.dss.xades.XPathQueryHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XAdES111XPathQueryHolder, XAdES122XPathQueryHolder

    public class XPathQueryHolder
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class hold all XPath queries schema-dependent. It was created to cope with old signatures bases on http://uri.etsi.org/01903/v1.1.1.
